videos.description: Nickeil Alexander-Walker slips a bounce pass through the Virginia defense to Ahmed Hill for the Virginia Tech slam.
videos.headline: Hill slams home nifty pass for Hokies

videos.description: Virginia Tech traps Ty Jerome at half court and Kerry Blackshear Jr. finishes the jam at the other end.
videos.headline: VA Tech turns steal into Blackshear dunk

videos.description: Virginia takes an errant pass the other way and Kyle Guy cleans up a missed layup with a dunk.
videos.headline: Virginia steal leads to Guy's putback slam

videos.description: Virginia Tech cuts Virginia's lead to three just before halftime as Isaiah Wilkins goes up-and-under for the lay-in.
videos.headline: Wilkins connects on crafty lay-in before half

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Jonathan Kabongo drives to the hoop and goes up strong for a layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Kabongo finishes and-1 layup

videos.description: Ahmed Hill steps in front of a Virginia pass and goes coast-to-coast for a powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Hill steals and flies for the slam

videos.description: Virginia's Mamadi Diakite is left all alone, but spikes the ball off the back of the rim in the final minute.
videos.headline: Diakite botches wide-open jam

videos.description: Virginia's Kyle Guy drains six 3-pointers and racks up 23 points as the Cavaliers survive to beat the Hokies 64-58.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Guy's 23 points lead Virginia past VA Tech) 2019/02/18 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Guy's 23 points lead Virginia past VA Tech
